    <script type="text/javascript" src="/common/js/default.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(function () {

            var siteType = $Util.getCookie("SITETYPE");

            switch (siteType) {
                case "KOMB":
                    location.href = "/m/Error.html";
                    break;
                case "ENMB":
                    location.href = "/m/Error.html";
                    break;
            }

        });
    </script>

</head>
<body class="error">
    <div class="errorWrap">
        <h1><img src="/images/common/error_logo.png" alt="s-oil" /></h1>
        <div class="errorCon st01">
            <p>현재 서비스 점검 중입니다. 이용에 불편을 드려 죄송하며, 더욱 개선된 서비스로 찾아뵙겠습니다.</p>
            <p>The system is currently under maintenance. We apologize for any inconvenience caused and look forward to serving you with better service.</p>
            <!--
            <dl class="info02">
                <dt>점검 기간</dt>
                <dd>2.24(월) 18:00 ~ 21:00</dd>
                <dt>Maintenance Period</dt>
                <dd>24 Feb. 18:00 ~ 21:00 (KST)</dd>
            </dl>
            -->
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>